wmsLayer.name: GA0315_huon_1m
wmsLayer.title: GA0315 Huon 1m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry grid of the survey area near the Huon River from marine survey GA0315, collected around Southeast Tasmania. The data is gridded at one metre resolution. A total of eight areas were surveyed at various resolutions. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 10-100 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/72003.
